'''Varns''' were wild predators found on [[Ibanjji]] that hunted in packs.<ref name="DESB">''[[Dark Empire Sourcebook]]''</ref>

When [[Titus Klev]] was 13, he was selected to attend a special [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR]] [[Sub-Adult Group/Legends|SAGroup]] motivational camp on Ibanjji, where he saved an instructor from a pack of varns. This got Klev approved to join [[CompForce/Legends|CompForce]] despite being four years younger than the standard enlistment age.<ref name="DESB" />

